|               |             RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([i_category@0, i_brand@1, cc_name@2, CAST(v1.rn AS Decimal128(20, 0))@9], 24), input_partitions=24                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |               ProjectionExec: expr=[i_category@0 as i_category, i_brand@1 as i_brand, cc_name@2 as cc_name, d_year@3 as d_year, d_moy@4 as d_moy, sum_sales@5 as sum_sales, avg_monthly_sales@6 as avg_monthly_sales, rn@7 as rn, sum_sales@8 as sum_sales, CAST(rn@7 AS Decimal128(20, 0)) as CAST(v1.rn AS Decimal128(20, 0))]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
